snippet.textDisplay: I can't stop listening to this song have been listening non-stop since I first heard it. This must be one of the best coke studio performances ever. The vocal quality is out of the world. Vishal Dadlani's power and Sonu Kakkar's high pitch just brings it to another dimension. Clinton Cerejo just realizes he has just made a masterpiece of a lifetime. I think Sonu Kakkar is a very underrated singer when compared with her sister Neha , she deserves way more spotlight and this song just proves it.
